---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - LingoDrip">
  <main class="py-24 px-4 min-h-screen mt-10">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="font-black text-4xl md:text-5xl text-panda-black mb-8 text-center">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      
      <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl border-2 border-panda-black shadow-card p-8 md:p-12">

        <div class="space-y-6">
          <p class="text-lg font-nunito text-panda-black/80 font-bold">Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString()}</p>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl text-panda-black mb-3">1. Introduction</h2>
            <p class="font-nunito text-panda-black/80 leading-relaxed">
              Your privacy is important to us. It is LingoDrip's policy to respect your
              privacy regarding any information we may collect from you across our website,
              and other sites we own and operate.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl text-panda-black mb-3">2. Information We Collect</h2>
            <p class="font-nunito text-panda-black/80 leading-relaxed">
              We only ask for personal information when we truly need it to provide a service
              to you. We collect it by fair and lawful means, with your knowledge and
              consent.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl text-panda-black mb-3">3. How We Use Information</h2>
            <p class="font-nunito text-panda-black/80 leading-relaxed">
              We use the information we collect to operate and maintain our specific services,
              improve your experience, and communicate with you.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl text-panda-black mb-3">4. Data Retention</h2>
            <p class="font-nunito text-panda-black/80 leading-relaxed">
              We only retain collected information for as long as necessary to provide you
              with your requested service. What data we store, we'll protect within
              commercially acceptable means to prevent loss and theft.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl text-panda-black mb-3">5. Sharing of Data</h2>
            <p class="font-nunito text-panda-black/80 leading-relaxed">
              We don't share any personally identifying information publicly or with
              third-parties, except when required to by law.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl text-panda-black mb-3">6. Your Rights</h2>
            <p class="font-nunito text-panda-black/80 leading-relaxed">
              You are free to refuse our request for your personal information, with the
              understanding that we may be unable to provide you with some of your desired
              services.
            </p>
          </section>

          <section>
            <h2 class="font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl text-panda-black mb-3">7. Contact Us</h2>
            <p class="font-nunito text-panda-black/80 leading-relaxed">
              If you have any questions about how we handle user data and personal
              information, feel free to contact us at privacy@lingodrip.com.
            </p>
          </section>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
